This folder contains scripts to run a penning-trap testcase in different grid layouts.
Use run.sh to compile and run a testcase (by using an optional filename argument) or all testcases (run without arguments).
See http://jorek.eu/wiki/doku.php?id=penning_test for more details about the testcase.

If one of the testcases fails, use gnuplot to load 'penning_error.gp' to see the scaling of the error.
